      <title>斯塔默称黛安·阿博特“可以”代表工党参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/starmer-says-diane-abbott-free-to-stand-for-labour-in-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前有报道称资深国会议员黛安·阿博特将被禁止参加英国大选，此举引发多日批评。基尔·斯塔默表示，资深国会议员黛安·阿博特可以“自由”作为工党候选人参加英国大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/starmer-says-diane-abbott-free-to-stand-for-labour-in-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 13:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
